## Arima and SArima models

Goals
-

- Understand timeseries data in detail
- Learn about timeseries data forecasting
- Learn how ARIMA and SARIMA work



Learning Objectives
- 

- Understand timeseries data forecasting
- Understand how ARIMA works
- Understand how SARIMA works
- Understand what is the difference between ARIMA and SARIMA
- Learn how to implement ARIMA and SARIMA in python
- Learn about advantages and disadvantages of the models
- Learn Applications of these models

Training Activities
-

- Run ARIMA with example data
- Run SARIMA with example data

